msgs.Content: *checks my email right before bed*
*email that's been sent to pretty much the entire school*
*watches the video wide eyed* no.......that's not.....that can't.......what?
*another email pops up, this time only to you* Is this really someone you think you should trust
.........soemthing's gonna die......... *immediately starts climbing out onto the roof*
*pacing in his room,
*trying not to start throwing things cuz is pretty pissed off*
*you can hear me jump across the chasm between our two houses*
*opens window and leans out* go back to bed it's a school night and you don't want to be here right now
no i think i do. *pulls out phone and shows the last email i got*
*scowls and whirls around* goddamit....
when?
Before you were born
that's impossible.......
You were never supposed to know.
*sitting on the window sill dangling my feet still kinda stuck on "before i was born" and applying every bit of vamp knowledge i have* but i remember you eating....your favorite cookies.....
I hid it in my pocket, you'd expect suspicious if I never at least pretended to eat around you
*processing a minute* ......did Elizabeth know?
Yes
*gives that squinty "really...." look*
She was the only one besides hellsing to know
And Destler, though that hardly matters now

*quiet shouty (if that makes sense. that really quiet hushed voice but is still somehow worse than yelling at you)* how the hell did he know?! 
Also she can know, but i can't? i who have kept every secret known to man! jealously guarded, i might add!
The hell if I know how he found out! I had to threaten him to keep his damned mouth shut, the whole point being to protect you from this. The last thing I wanted was for you to get involved in this
*head in palm* that email went out to everyone...
and when i'm done being mad at you for lying to me, i'll be blasting Alice Cooper and having a bit of a vampaboo moment......
I know. And be as mad as you like you were safe and you weren't scared so as far as I'm concerned I was doing the right thing

god you thought i'd be scared of you? i, who would love to get my hands on Pinhead's box? have we met me? i couldn't be scared of you if you tried to terrify me yourself! i'd just toss pillows at you until burried.
*facepalm* as a child you would've been, and as you grew up it became more of a fact of you not having to deal with learning what you'd known all your life was wrong
and as tall as you are you still fail to catch my point.
You're making this harder and harder to be pissed about
i know.
not for me tho.
*pinches the bridge of his nose* I'm gonna kill them. I am going to kill every single one of them
How did they even get the video
can't kill them. it's high school
Fine I'll make them wish they were dead
thaaaaat's much better
I'm going to shove his drumsticks so far down his throat.....
can i help?
Please do, it'll be so much more satisfying for them to know their little stunt did nothing to scare you away
*wicked little smile*
*smirks and pats your head* Glad to see you're following a good example
you expected anything else? i'll be scared of Mac before i'm scared of you.
Good. So what will we do to them first
i would like evil busty lesbian's head on a platter...........but that's out of the question too....... mean i don't know them enough to really exact the kind of revenge this warrants......
what if we could make them think it worked?
At the moment all my ideas end with them in the hospital but I want them to suffer before that
And then?
i mean i could info gather w/ that......
Lie would need to know the plan.....if she's in the dark it's all over.....
Why?
How could she mess up the plan if she's unaware of it
cause she'd have Erik get to the bottom of it. possibly using Giovanni to do so...
Fine, don't let her mess this up
oh she wouldn't. might even be able to enlist help.......
And this is all assuming she is unaffected by this and Destler doesn't keep her out of it
she has all those men wrapped around her little finger. pretty sure she can get them to do anything she wants. my shit is her shit always has been.
Fine, if you have faith in her and think she can help, talk to her about it
But it's a school night still do for now, you need to to go bed
give me 10 mins. *goes back out on the roof and dials*
*answers* hey
so did you check your email?
Not yet, I just finished rinsing out due, why?
*dye

spoiler alert, it's horrifying. Major Payne in my ass is trying to split me and Vlad up for some weird vendetta idk....we're gonna make him think it worked so i can find out some information about what we're dealing w/. and then we're gonna fuck their world up....
Sounds like a plan, the
after i'm done being mad at idjit.
*though how is this gonna go? You just gonna start staying away from him or go straight to them
And why are you mad at him

probably go straight to them. turn on the water works. pull a "how the hell could he" probably stage public fight.....
it......it's probably best if you just watch the tape.
.....Is it possibly related to whatever Erik was so bent outta shape about?
*today?
yeah....yousa mighten be sayin that.
*long pause* ...... I see why there is anger and concern
yep. he lied to me, granted to try to keep me away from it. so now he's Idjit until such a time as i'm not angry.
Understandable.
but now you know the plan. i need to go to bed before he carries me there himself.
Thanks for letting me know. Sleep good, see you tomorrow
you too. *hangs up and goes back to the window* you're now Idjit until such a time as i've become un-angry. now i'm going to bed.
I can accept that, go on, sleep well *pats your head*
night Idjit. *runs back across the roof/chasm and goes to bed*
*gets up a little later than normal, awaking to the sound of Sir Valiant pulling from the drive* yay.......
*pokes her head in* how come he didn't wait for you?
not going in w/ him.
Why not?
i'm a big girl, i can be left alone for a bit *looking through my closet*
You got another ride?
gonna actually ride the bus.
Okay then, don't miss it
*not a skirt this time, but still all black and comes down for breakfast*
*hands her a plate*
thank you *starts in* did Mac spend the night?
No, he left pretty late though
*nods*
*grabbing stuff for work* you got all your forms right?
yeah i do. *finishes and grabs my bag, going outside to wait* i'll see you later this afternoon mama.
Have a good day
you too
*bus comes and picks you up*
*cautiously finds a seat amid all the whispers*
*to school*
*glances back to Sir Valiant before making way over to Mina*
*Glances up* I see you got the email
who did it?
Major
*turning to him* how the hell'd you get video? they don't show up in mirrors, shouldn't show up on video either...
No idea
*marching right up to asshole* well?
Well what?
how'd you do it?
I'd tell you, but it's a secret
maybe it's a secret i need if i'm gonna stake the bastard.
*raises an eyebrow as if surprised* That seems drastic for someone you were so close to
probably just keeping me for spare blood right?
It's hard to say
i mean that's the only conclusion i can come to. i haven't seen the Lost Boys 15 million times for nothing.
Things like him shouldn't be allowed near humans, should they?
depends on the vamp.
i mean there's Louis....
Who?
Interview w/.....nvm.
Either way, you mentioned wanting to get back at him?
clean your ears. i said i want him re-dead.
*Grin* Why don't you join us for lunch then, and we can discuss this further
*bellrings* fine.
Till then
*goes to class, texting in my pocket* _phase one complete. i'm in_
/Good/
*watching* did what just happened.......happen?

*In Arabic cuz doesn't want to risk exposing plan* 'innah wahid 'an tursil risalatan 'iilaa muhawalat litahwil faliri didd filad , hatta 'annahum alllaeb jnba 'iilaa janb lilhusul ealaa aleawda (He's the one that sent the email to try to turn Valerie against Vlad, so they're playing along to get back)
*nods* that makes sense.
Do you think you can help or at least go along with it?
oh of course i can
just go back to normal it's simple
Just don't go stirring up trouble
now would i do that?
*At the same time as Lie* yes
both of you lack any idea of fun.
I just like not getting yelled at by teachers
oh it's hardly yelling.
Still exactly fun, though some of your ideas are worth it
at least someone thinks so.
*trying not to glance back as i walk passed the table and goes to the Band corner*
the hell is she doing here?
She's learned what kind of monster he was, and wants to put an end to him
you believe her?
Not yet
then what is she doing here? *accent thickening*
We'll see soon enough, for now, try to play nice with her tho
nice is not in m vocabulary
Then try not to chase them away *nods to Lie joining up with Val*
uuughhh both of them?!
It would seem so
hey....
How is your day going? *small talk*
could be better
I hope no one's given you a hard time about him
*shrugs* i think ppl are still scared. looked after me for 6 years. always said if he found a single tear, someone would lose a head.
I see. Well at least that makes things easier for you
*leans on Lie* why're you over here and not w/ the brothers?
Giovanni wanted to see them, and I'm not really in the mood for hearing "I told you so" again
understandable....
sorry i didn't ask him in the first place.....
He did say Vlad threatened him if he said anything
for the love of....
so does wood work, or are we dealing w/ straight silver?
Wood works if it goes through the heart, silver's better though
*making small notes* as much as i've assembled through years of research, there's so much lore to pile through...
It does make things more difficult
how did you learn?
Lot's of research and some friends
oh.
So what did you have in mind besides simply staking him
honestly that's all it would take to get my frustrations out.
And if you fail to end him?
oh i won't.
If you're confident you won't
and there's no one more confident than me.
Alright then
should we be worried that he can withstand daylight?
I think we simply can't underestimate him
so silver knife, and do the whole nine yards..
That's what I would go with
i'll bring the mathes.
matches**
I'd remember kerosene, just in case
how we getting passed Hellsing?
That, my dear, is the trick
isn't it? she doesn't let shit go...
And she takes action quickly
i mean i'm normally in and out of the house....
I wasn't aware you were quite so close, that complicates things
Miss In.....Hellsing used to babysit me.
and she lets me crash there, for reasons.
I see
but dragging anyone else....tough
*nods*
and i guess it's my issue isn't it.....
I'm afraid so
so i know how this goes.
And how does it go?
my problem. my point to take care of it.
Alright
great.......*looking not so enthused...
It'll get better
yeah. i bet.
*goes to hug her* he tricked us all. Elizabeth included.
*moves* ok. i have rules and rule #1 is no touching. i don't touch. no one touches me.
ok...*backs up* fine. sorry....
Noted
*bell rings and i dart*
*Everyone heads to class*
*walking by Vlad and hisses* ei te vor mort
(they want you dead)
Asta e drastic (That's drastic)
*turns back* și ei mă trimit să o fac. (and they're sending me to do it.)
*Irritated sigh and turns too* Deci, ei sunt prea frică să se încerce, jalnic (So they're too afraid to do it themselves, pathetic
Cea mai mare parte pentru că eu sunt singurul care se poate ajunge în casă! (Mostly because I'm the only one who can get in the house!)
*Scoffs* Cu toate acestea, ei trimit boboc de a ucide fiara, e doar trist (Still, they're sending the freshman to kill the beast, that's just sad)
ar putea fi mai rău, vreau să spun că știu cum .... (could be worse, i mean i know how....) *tries to walk away*
*Grabs your arm and voice starts getting loud and aggressive* Ce mai faci? Oricine se joacă cu tine? (So, how are you doing? Anyone messing with you?)
*jerks away and shouts* lesbiene mari tittied, dar asta e de așteptat! (big tittied lesbian, but that's expected!)
*gets in your face* Ce? (What the?)
*forming a fist* Păr blond! germană accent! (Blonde hair! german accent!)
*Grabs your wrist* Știi, chiar dacă ea este lesbiană? (Do you even know if she's a lesbian?)
*pulls it back* nu, dar ea se uită la Seras ca și băieții se uite la fete!(no but she looks at Seras like boys look at girls!)
foarte atent! (Very observant)
Am trăit cu tine timp de 6 ani!(i lived with you for 6 years!)
A trebuit să fie mai mare de șase (Had to be longer than six)
Nu a fost de 6! Astăzi.(No it was 6! Today.)
*runs up before Vlad can yell anything else ((had to switch to iPod which doesn't like google translate))* Hey, leave her alone! *pulls you back*
it's fine Lie. i'm just leaving. *glares*
*glares, face says murder but eyes say "that actually worked out well"* I recommend you mind your own buisiness *growling*
Then pick on someone your own damn size.
my shit is her shit. *links arms and off to class*
Well that went well *fake sarcasm*
surprisingly. better than i'd hoped.
I really don't like them though, how long do we have to play nice?
not sure......
Okay
but i know what everyone wants.
And that is?
oh death, destruction, the fall of humanity...
So much for peace, love and planet earth ((*proceeds to have that song stuck in my head for he rest of the night*))
yep.......miss the car....
Want me to ask if we can give you a ride home, you'd have to stay after a while, but it's not the bus
it's not that. it's more.......i love that car...
Oh I understand
yeah....but i'll see you after class ok?
Okay *waves before heading off*
*goes to class extremely aware of whispers*
*class*
*sitting in the back like normal. last class*
*is an aid for said class and walks up to you* would you mind helping me get the last of the packets together for the class *excuse*
.......you know what why the hell not.
*leads the way to the office for that department* your name is Valeriana, right?
Valerie.
Valerie *correcting himself* I heard about the.... Situation
and i can handle it

*sets out papers for the packets and staplers* I do not doubt that, but I heard about the issue after lunch and I wanted to tell you, if you ever have concern for your safety over this, or you're worried he may come after you, let me know, there are places where you'd be safe
thanks. not scared of him. i've seen worse.
Still, be careful
i will. i mean i've survived for 6 years...
Again, I just wanted to tell you. Even if you never need the help, it's better you have the option than not in case things change
thanks.
*Nods* What do you think of your classes *trying to lighten things with small talk*
meh. could be worse, i mean it's class....
Are there any you like? An elective maybe?
*shrugs* getting the ones i need to graduate out of the way first.
Smart move
it was Miss Hellsing's suggestion.
Ah, I see
so basically i just have to suffer through *stapling*
It gets better after the first year
yeah that's what i hear
And then everything goes downhill again in senior year *kinda joking*
heh
*Smiles, getting last packet done* Thanks, if you just want to take them on your way back, and if you ever need me, this is where I am during this period the majority of the time
got it. see you *takes the rest of them and takes them all back w/ me and gives them to the teacher*
*Teacher thanks you and passes them out as class starts*
*after last class, climbs up on the bus and picks an empty seat*
*Text* /Two band people live down the street/
_seriously! there goes hiding in your room and planning_
/I'll skype you at home/
/And all the more reason to not waste time/
_exactly. i may have an idea that goes along w/ the fight this afternoon._
/What is it?/
_i'll tell you on skype. still refining._
*shifts and hides my phone quick*
*pulls out of parking lot*
*puts my earphones in while i feel someone sink into the seat next to me*
*bright smile* Hey! *doesn't understand the code of the headphone*
*pulls one out* hi?
I don't think we had proper introduction, I'm Rip!
Valerie, nice to meet you. so....what do you play?
Flute, what kinda stuff are you into?
*shrugs* i read a lot. and i play a little paintball.
That's cool! I've never done paint ball before
its just as much mental as it is physical.
That sounds great!
like dodgeball, but w/ guns.
Oh Zorin would definitely love that
what's her deal anyway?
She just doesn't like new people
i mean she's been after my ass since day one.
A bit of it is him too, and Seras
figured him......and......eh she's cute.
Yeah, she's alright
so what's the band working on for halftime shows?
Oh it's great! We're doing *some pieces idk*
i've never actually heard that one
It's awesome
guess i'll have to catch it then.
You should our half times are great
is Mina in the band too?
No, she's dating the major
i always heard about her but i didn't get to actually meet her....
She's not bad
yeah he always said she was sweet.....*small smile* probably need to get out of that too.
Take your time, it's only been a day
eh you're right. 6 years is a long time to get over. ok........busty lesbian really givin you the stink eye.......just saying.
*looks* oh, it's just cuz I'm sitting with you, she'll get over it
just don't wanna cause anything.
It's fine
*bus stops* this is me. *gets up and goes home.*
See ya! *waves*
*shivers as i step off the bus* that was a revolting encounter
*Text* /Bus takes forever, I pity you/
*smiles going in the house* _go get a nap...._
/Can't, Hellsing says I gotta clean up the house like I'm her maid/
_ugh. i don't envy you. at least it's kinda.......empty in here._
/Least he's not there/
_small blessings. so emergency maneuver: anything happens i'm barricading my room and going around back where the woods are_
/If worst comes to worst I'll send someone for you/
_but this is like.....drunken rage prep. just in case_
/I know, just in case/
_do your chores. i have homework_
/let me know if something happens/
_i will_
*goes and does her homework, computer right next to me*
*later calls her*
*hits the video icon, still kinda sitting here working*
What are you on?
not homework.
i kinda have a paintball game this weekend
Working on a plan for that?
yeah. but yeah there's two ways we can do this staking thing...
And they are?
before i go into that. glamoring. that possible?
Yeah, the more weak minded someone is, the easier it is to control their mind

we can either have you skip a couple days, say i staked you one night, by myself. reveal at school and embarrass the hell out of them. or we can take the acting up a notch and do it in a place where they all can see. and well i mean you gotta defend yourself somehow....
Second plan. It'll be much more interesting
so where do we do this? i mean......cant do it at school Miss Integra'll have a farm...
Isn't there a football game Friday?
should be. again. Miss Integra'll have a farm....
*frowns* then what do you suggest? (he wanted to be the new halftime show)
can you handle her?
w/o getting anyone expelled?
Of course, it's easy. All I have to do is say I wanted to scare the little brats
ok. fine you can be the halftime show.
*Smirks* This'll be good
and i was right about busty lesbian
Of course
goin after Victoria.
*debating telling him about Mina and the drum major*
That'll be interesting
and not our problem.
It'll be fine to watch from the sidelines
Busty Lesbian's also one of the ones that lives near me.
Of course. Nothing about this can be simple can it?
nope. her and a girl Rip. tiny. shouldn't really make a fuss
I see
but the other one.......she's been after me from day one. she's gonna be a little bit harder and kinda more paranoid
You can handle it
yeah....just a week of this. that's all we got...
Thank god
so do we tell Miss Integra?
Does she have to know beforehand?
well no. was just thinking it might give her a nice heads up....
Well if she ever finds out about the "Fight"...
*hasn't even sat down for first period*
*Over the intercom* Will Valeriana Barks and Vladamir Dracul please report to the office
............shit. *about face and walk right back out the door*
*At the office when you get there*
*sitting at her desk as they come in* Valerie. sit.
*sits* ok....
the hell is going on w/ you two?
I plead the fifth
i invoke my right to silence
*head in hand* of course you do.
*Smirks*
look. i don't know what you did to her but you're apologizing.
You always assume it's my fault
i doubt she would have done it since she's the one making longing glances when she thinks no one's looking
Not my fault she's fallen hopelessly in love with me *Sarcastic shiteating smirk*
*pinches the bridge of her nose* jesus chri.........i can either get it from you two or i can get it from your friends.
What friends?
she has friends. don't think i haven't noticed you've made enemies. and don't think i haven't noticed she's been w/ them.
That's speculation
like hell it is.
So they're probably jealous
you're missing my point.
You had a point?
that we're going to fix whatever's been done so i can sleep at night.
If we tell you you'll lose even more
*looking at Valeria* please talk sense......
i have the right to remain silent.....
*smirks at her like "what can you do?"*
neither of you are leaving this office until you tell me what's going on here.
You act like we want to go to class
you will lose that car...
We didn't start it
cât de mult să-i spunem? (how much do we tell her?)
*in Romanian (cuz iPod)* /just that there were rumors, and we're making fools of them/
*glares* you 're teaching her very rude habits...
I'm teaching her how to determine what others need to know and what they don't
then who did start it? *obviously very tired of his shit*
*looks to you for whether you think she should know*
band kids. they're after him. don't ask me idk. and we have it handled. you just have to keep worrying for less than a week. we can't be seen together, unless one of us is screaming at the other.
like yesterday
what was that?
information passing.
And a bit of small talk
*still pinching the bridge of her nose* can't you two put those skills to better use?
I fail to see any better use
drama department could use a hand
not my thing. nope.
Destler  wouldn't be happy to see me there
and he'll only sing for me....
/thanks for just blowing that open/
_oh hush she's heard it. and it's cute_
i'm trying to figure out when you taught her romanian...
like six years ago. everytime you left us alone...
why do i ask questions anymore.
I've been wondering for years /and bullshit nothing about me is cute/
_you're fucking adorable you fucking adorable fuck!_
*glares a tiny bit* /least I'm not like you, five foot nothing and adorable as all fucking hell/
_no you're that tol kinda adorable that doesn't know what to do w/ himself!_
enough!
/If you weren't so adorable I'd kick your ass for that/ okay now we're done
go. just go. idc if you go back to class, just go!
*Smirks and walks out*
*waits a bit, then goes back to class*
*lerking up in the catwalks after hours*
*Goes up for her audition for the play*
*doesn't really look twice at the little whisp of a thing
*Sings, not perfect but still*
*sits down and listens a bit*
*Goes down when she's done and Carlotta goes up*
*stays hidden but catches her backs stage* that was very good
*Surprised, but smiles politely* O-Oh, thank you
i can help it be better.
*Blinks then brightens* Really? I'd really appreciate that! Even if you could help a little that'd be so amazing
you're new aren't you?
Kinda, I moved her over the summer
*here
why don't we meet here, once a week? wednesdays?
That'd be great!
I gotta go, my friend's giving me a ride home, but I'll see you wednesday! *Waves as she jogs off*
*smiles* wednesday....
*finds him* What's got you all happy?
nothing dear. come on. lets save your ears.
*mumbles* it's not "nothing if it's got you smiling right before Carlotta sings *leaves theater area with him before Carlotta can get going*
someone just killed better than she did is all
Pretty sure anyone could, so tell me about this one
long honey curls. voice like an angel..... eyes like tea in the sunlight....
*lights up* you have a crush! That's so adorable!
i do not
You do I can see it in your eyes *swings his hand* You two could sing duets together!
i do not have a crush!
You just get all dreamy eyed whenever you describe girls
i did not go dreamy eyed!
*mimics his look* voice like an angel and eyes like tea in the sunlight.....
you little *grabs her and tosses her over his shoulder*
Hey! What are you doing?
you gonna hush or do i have to spin
Last time you did that we nearly took out Nadir, and I won't stop until you admit you have a crush on her
*steps into a twirl*
*clings for dear life* you're an ass
*pauses* done?
For now.... But this isn't over
*sets her down* it had better be
*grabs his arm cuz dizzy* you gotta learn how to admit you're feelings
nope.
See this is the kinda stuff you do when you have the nightmares you never talk about it and we can't help you. You gotta open up some
oh just you being there helps the nightmares
*sighs* either way, even if you won't admit it, thank you cuz that bit of adorableness cuz now I'm happy again
good. *gets back to giovanni's room*
Good. *runs in* ERIK HAS A CRUSH ON A GIRL FROM AUDITIONS *hides behind Nadir*
god.....damnit girl
*blinks and looks back at her as she darts behind him then at Erik* what?
Erik said he met a girl with beautiful hair, eyes and a beautiful voice and it's adorable
*grabs her and covers her mouth*  i think Rosalie might be a little feverish!
*struggling and muffled argument*
*"seriously?" Look* she has a fever so you restrain her
dear. dear we can't hear you.
*licks his hand to make him let go*
ew! *really wants to pull away, but doesn't*
*slight snicker* Let her go before she tries worse
oh like she will
*reaches around and tickles his side* *muffled "I will not be tamed!"*
ah! shit! *lets go*
Victory! *darts back behind Nadir before wiping her mouth* your hands tastes gross
then don't lick it.
Don't cover my mouth to try to hide the truth
learn to hold your tongue.
Nah, much more fun this way. Plus you were the one who always told me to speak my mind
you always missed "when appropriate" in that lesson
And you didn't?
no. no i didn't
And why are you so ashamed about liking a girl? There's no shame in having a crush
i do not have a crush
he does he got all dreamy eyed when he talked about her and he was smiling before Carlotta sang
alright you little rat
*ducks back, hanging on to Nadir for protection*
you can't keep running to him. one day he's not gonna be here.
Would rather I run to Valerie and/or Vlad?
Besides, I'm not overly fond of trying to walk while dizzy
not while they're fighting.
There's always Gio too
you're not cute
*scoffs* already knew that buddy, I told you before, Nadir's mom friend, your talented friend, I'm potato friend
as in you're not getting away with that.
I'll make sure I stay up tonight
good idea.
But you watch out cuz I'll find out who she is
you will not
How am I gonna help set you two up if I don't know who she is
you will do no such thing!
Try to stop me, even if I stay outta this I still wanna know who she is
you will find out. later.
Promise?
promise
But you're still gonna try for payback, aren't you
eh
Even if I promise to stay outta it
we know you can't
I won't do anything to much. Talking to her at most, promise
